{"tid":2514076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「懲罰Mee」app　未正式推出就已經跑贏左 #安心出行","createTime":"2021-05-03T04:29:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T04:58:13.000Z","uid":261647,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a2717e606c04630d1f96ed0f0f0d649bad8ba604","tid":2514076,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:29:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Mee.punishC/posts/225207266030244\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMee.punishC%2Fposts%2F225207266030244&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOCfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=d054acbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Mee.punishC/posts/225207266030244</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPDwbrUuCVHDuyBSs4jARLBRVmsgqNbtkJtvfVUSk6yrQ?filename=7sv7KEv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7sv7KEv.png&h=b3401a7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：Mee 懲罰師<br />\n<br />\n真係冇諗過，都未正式推出就已經跑贏左 #安心出行，香港人就係咁勁！<br />\n<br />\n無錯，「懲罰Mee」app唔止係半年前嘅一個玩笑，今日終於正式推出。早幾日我地靜雞雞放左上App Store俾大家「試玩」，估唔到已經成為香港區排行榜第一名。<br />\n<br />\n不過呢件事一定唔可以只係三分鐘熱度，「懲罰Mee」嘅長遠目標，就係要打破代表大企業小圈子的 #Yuu 同 支付寶持有的 #OpenRice 嘅壟斷。<br />\n<br />\nMee相信，香港人即使要捱，都要捱得有腰骨。<br />\n<br />\n今次大家可以在「懲罰Mee」的地圖中，非常方便地尋找到這次參與「5.1懲罰祭」的商戶。只要成為Mee會員，大家就可以到這些良心小店享有95折優惠或其他獨家優惠。<br />\n<br />\n以後大家唔洗再喺Yuu儲分，可以儲「Mee分」！「Mee分」唔會同消費掛勾，亦唔會記低大家嘅消費紀錄同習慣。好多嘢係用錢都買唔到，我哋希望透過「Mee分」鼓勵大家，繼續係生活入面共行互助。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以透過上載照片、寫食評等方式，在儲「Mee分」的同時，協助豐富app內的資訊，加強黃色經濟圈資訊流通，令香港人唔再需要依賴類似Openrice等嘅中資大型平台。<br />\n<br />\n感謝 終極黃藍地圖<br />\n團隊在籌備階段的協助，讓團隊能夠建立基本的黃店數據庫；也感謝許多良心小店的踴躍報名與耐心等候。由於收到大量的商戶的報名，團隊現時仍在全速整理報名參與商戶的資訊，希望能夠盡快於「懲罰Mee」app內更新不同店鋪的資料。<br />\n<br />\n請大家狠狠地懲罰Mee，等我哋狠狠地懲罰Yuu。<br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n最後要同用Android機嘅朋友講聲唔好意思👇<br />\n由於 Google Play 於四月中更新了審批政策，「懲罰Mee」在 Google Play 的審批已拖了一段時間，希望能夠盡快正式上架。大家暫時可以透過以下的連結，或掃描黃店內實體文宣上的QR code直接下載 APK 檔，就可以在Android平台上使用「懲罰Mee」，我們會爭取在「5.1懲罰祭」期間完成上架。<br />\n<br />\niOS（建議重裝）👉 <a href=\"https://link.meeapp.com/ios\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flink.meeapp.com%2Fios&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOCfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=1c730ec3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://link.meeapp.com/ios</a><br />\nAndroid（已有更新，請使用瀏覽器下載）👉<a href=\"https://link.meeapp.com/android\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flink.meeapp.com%2Fandroid&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOCfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=ae46fdee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://link.meeapp.com/android</a>"},{"pid":"37a0713e154df5b4160b94958eb7b4da7da2cdc6","tid":2514076,"uid":123591,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:30:50.000Z","msg":"但個app好垃圾下"},{"pid":"4a9b92f63fd2938f0b16e620cddd4ce7a467b67a","tid":2514076,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"我部機係咪太舊 出亂碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2bc4d00e4efe4fa479a064b1ceb9a77b17dbcfc","tid":2514076,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"但點知間野係咪黃，定加入mee 就心照？"},{"pid":"977eece5a9367bea0ea335e631be1a3364f3aaa7","tid":2514076,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:51:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9d820e29324d64f07b9bfe947ad4e55c8d1ec684","tid":2514076,"uid":133534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:57:44.000Z","msg":"想知Mee 裡面啲黃店係根據乜原則定出嚟？<br />\n<br />\n我見灣仔再興燒味係和你play 係綠<br />\n<br />\n但係Mee 係黃<br />\n<br />\n黃定綠？"},{"pid":"5815911e81199caeb9f3e7cd83698af0ec4b89e3","tid":2514076,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}